Key-words appearing on Title line of MulVib
===========================================

#info		Info-only-run. Stops after evaluation of basis states.
#restart	Continue Lanczos iterations from previous run.
#nosave		Do not save data for further restart.
#noplot		Do not produce plot data.

#full		Full diagonalization instaed of Lanczos (testing?).
#nosym		Turns off symmetry. This is not clear, whaether
		this option works, and whether it makes sence
		to use it for treating coupling of several states
		of the same symmetry (since the formalism of 2x2
		linear coupling model may be invalid in such a case,
		especcially concernig algorithm for derivaton of
		lambda constants). ABT 15-02-2015

#debug		General debugging option.

Extended print out for specific programs:

#initz		initz.
#input		input.
#mtcor		mtcor.
#mult_tst	lacor.
#mulvib		mulvib.
      
#fuldg		fuldg.
#h-mat		fulldg option.
#h-vec		fulldg option.	
#h-eig		fulldg option.	

